{"word":"H2680 - חֲצִי הַמְּנַחְתִּי - Chătsîy ham-Mᵉnachtîy - khat-see' ham-menakh-tee' - Half of the Manahethites","slug":"H2680","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חֲצִי הַמְּנַחְתִּי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Chătsîy ham-Mᵉnachtîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khat-see' ham-menakh-tee'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Half of the Manahethites"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05E6;&#x05D9; &#x05D4;&#x05DE;&#x05BC;&#x05E0;&#x05D7;&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05D9; - cha&#x0306;ts&#x0131;&#x0302;y hamm<sup>e</sup>nacht&#x0131;&#x0302;y</b> - <i>khat-see' ham-men-akh-tee'</i><p/>Patronymic from <a href=\"#/H2679\">H2679</a>; a <i>Chatsi ham-Menachtite</i> or descendant of Chatsi ham-menuchoth: - half of the Manahethites."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2010\">H2010</a>, <a href=\"#/H2679\">H2679</a>, <a href=\"#/H3239\">H3239</a>, <a href=\"#/H3240\">H3240</a>, <a href=\"#/H4494\">H4494</a>, <a href=\"#/H4495\">H4495</a>, <a href=\"#/H4496\">H4496</a>, <a href=\"#/H4506\">H4506</a>, <a href=\"#/H5117\">H5117</a>, <a href=\"#/H5118\">H5118</a>, <a href=\"#/H5119\">H5119</a>, <a href=\"#/H5146\">H5146</a>, <a href=\"#/H5183\">H5183</a>, <a href=\"#/H5207\">H5207</a>"}]}